1
00:00:00,868 --> 00:00:02,336
♪

2
00:00:02,936 --> 00:00:06,973
Narrator: Meanwhile, as gon
was summoning every last ounce

3
00:00:06,974 --> 00:00:10,210
of his power to finally
finish off neferpitou,

4
00:00:10,210 --> 00:00:13,113
meruem, pouf, and youpi
were gathered together

5
00:00:13,146 --> 00:00:17,417
inside the west tower,
where komugi had recently been.

6
00:00:41,542 --> 00:00:43,277
Shaiapouf: This is it.

7
00:00:52,986 --> 00:00:55,655
West tower, second floor.

8
00:00:55,722 --> 00:00:57,924
If we can
just clear this area,

9
00:00:57,991 --> 00:01:01,194
the king will have
forgotten her forever.

10
00:01:03,931 --> 00:01:06,066
I can’t allow him
any opportunities

11
00:01:06,133 --> 00:01:07,635
where he might see her.

12
00:01:12,673 --> 00:01:13,607
♪

13
00:01:13,674 --> 00:01:15,609
( Singing in Japanese )

14
00:01:57,317 --> 00:01:59,252
♪

15
00:02:18,572 --> 00:02:20,407
Meruem: Something is missing.

16
00:02:23,243 --> 00:02:26,446
But just what is it?

17
00:02:29,216 --> 00:02:31,151
I do not know.

18
00:02:31,218 --> 00:02:32,519
( Shaiapouf gasps )

19
00:02:34,721 --> 00:02:38,258
Menthuthuyoupi: I know,
and you’re absolutely right.

20
00:02:38,325 --> 00:02:40,460
I’m not gonna tell him.

21
00:02:40,527 --> 00:02:43,063
I don’t want her
around the king either.

22
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:45,032
( Coughs )

23
00:02:46,233 --> 00:02:49,336
I just--i want us
to stay this way.

24
00:02:51,171 --> 00:02:55,175
Meruem: How curious.
It would seem that this feeling,

25
00:02:55,242 --> 00:02:57,511
the feeling
something is missing,

26
00:02:57,578 --> 00:03:00,581
may simply be
a symptom of amnesia,

27
00:03:00,647 --> 00:03:03,416
a side effect
of my current condition.

28
00:03:04,685 --> 00:03:06,120
( Shaiapouf gasps )

29
00:03:06,186 --> 00:03:08,021
Of course it is, sire.

30
00:03:08,088 --> 00:03:10,057
Your memory
can easily be verified

31
00:03:10,123 --> 00:03:12,592
through what you can see
with your own two eyes,

32
00:03:12,659 --> 00:03:15,228
and that means
you should be able to recover

33
00:03:15,295 --> 00:03:17,531
all of the memories you need.

34
00:03:19,466 --> 00:03:21,234
Meruem: I believe
that the selection

35
00:03:21,301 --> 00:03:22,636
was to begin at 12:00?

36
00:03:22,703 --> 00:03:25,539
Shaiapouf: Yes, sire.
However, it can be moved up

37
00:03:25,606 --> 00:03:27,274
if that is your wish.

38
00:03:27,341 --> 00:03:30,144
By 9:00, the remaining humans

39
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:33,246
will all be gathered
on the plain before the palace.

40
00:03:34,715 --> 00:03:36,250
( Gasps )

41
00:03:36,316 --> 00:03:37,584
Meruem: What is it now?

42
00:03:37,651 --> 00:03:39,419
Shaiapouf:
I haven’t used my scales

43
00:03:39,486 --> 00:03:42,656
on the humans who are
still on their way in.

44
00:03:42,723 --> 00:03:45,059
We don’t want them
to cause a commotion,

45
00:03:45,125 --> 00:03:47,194
so I will summon
all of my segments

46
00:03:47,261 --> 00:03:49,930
and use them to hypnotize them.

47
00:03:49,997 --> 00:03:52,166
What about you, youpi?

48
00:03:52,232 --> 00:03:53,266
( Menthuthuyoupi groans )

49
00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:55,368
Let me think.

50
00:03:55,435 --> 00:03:58,204
- Guess i’ll look for pitou.
- ( Meruem gasps )

51
00:03:58,272 --> 00:04:00,641
Menthuthuyoupi: I don’t have
the strength to protect you,

52
00:04:00,707 --> 00:04:03,944
not the way I am
right now, anyway.

53
00:04:04,011 --> 00:04:05,212
Meruem: Pitou.

54
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:07,615
♪

55
00:04:07,681 --> 00:04:11,118
Shaiapouf: Did you
just remember something, sire?

56
00:04:11,185 --> 00:04:13,187
Menthuthuyoupi: Oh, yeah.
I completely forgot.

57
00:04:13,253 --> 00:04:15,622
We haven’t told the king
anything about pitou yet.

58
00:04:15,689 --> 00:04:17,357
Shaiapouf: Lord meruem,

59
00:04:17,424 --> 00:04:21,161
do you happen
to remember who pitou is?

60
00:04:21,228 --> 00:04:25,232
Meruem: I do. One of
my three personal royal guards.

61
00:04:25,299 --> 00:04:29,603
I can recall pitou’s appearance
so clearly.

62
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:32,606
In fact,
it seems rather unusual

63
00:04:32,673 --> 00:04:35,643
that I wouldn’t
have remembered it before now.

64
00:04:35,709 --> 00:04:37,311
( Shaiapouf gasps )

65
00:04:37,377 --> 00:04:40,513
So it isn’t just images
that can trigger his memory.

66
00:04:40,581 --> 00:04:42,650
Words can as well.

67
00:04:42,716 --> 00:04:46,153
We cannot let him hear her name.

68
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:48,656
We must be very careful.

69
00:04:48,722 --> 00:04:52,960
The key to this
will be convincing pitou.

70
00:04:54,728 --> 00:04:57,030
Menthuthuyoupi:
I know. Don’t worry.

71
00:04:57,097 --> 00:04:58,632
I won’t mention her.

72
00:05:00,701 --> 00:05:05,206
( High-pitched whine )

73
00:05:05,272 --> 00:05:07,174
Meruem: There it is again.

74
00:05:09,676 --> 00:05:12,212
( In memory )
I’m counting on you, pitou.

75
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,413
( Gasps )

76
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:16,383
Yes, that’s right.

77
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:20,421
I-I asked pitou
to do something for me,

78
00:05:20,487 --> 00:05:22,456
but what was it?

79
00:05:30,197 --> 00:05:31,198
Youpi.

80
00:05:31,265 --> 00:05:32,366
Menthuthuyoupi: Sire?

81
00:05:32,432 --> 00:05:34,401
Meruem: Bring pitou
to me immediately.

82
00:05:34,468 --> 00:05:36,136
We have things to discuss.

83
00:05:36,203 --> 00:05:37,404
Menthuthuyoupi: Right.

84
00:05:37,471 --> 00:05:40,140
Shaiapouf: And what will you do,
lord meruem?

85
00:05:40,207 --> 00:05:43,944
I ask, because there are
still enemies around.

86
00:05:44,011 --> 00:05:46,447
Meruem: So there are.

87
00:05:46,513 --> 00:05:48,949
I will go and search
for pitou myself

88
00:05:49,016 --> 00:05:51,952
and hunt the stragglers
in the process.

89
00:05:52,019 --> 00:05:54,321
( Shaiapouf gasps ) This is bad.

90
00:05:56,523 --> 00:05:58,959
Eh, sire, that would be, uh...

91
00:05:59,026 --> 00:06:02,096
Meruem: It is merely
for entertainment,

92
00:06:02,162 --> 00:06:05,565
and I am certain that they
have useful information.

93
00:06:05,632 --> 00:06:08,568
Shaiapouf: Perhaps,
but we won’t be at your side,

94
00:06:08,635 --> 00:06:10,570
and we don’t know
what enemies still remain.

95
00:06:10,637 --> 00:06:11,905
( Yelps )

96
00:06:11,972 --> 00:06:13,874
( Gasps )

97
00:06:13,941 --> 00:06:15,910
♪

98
00:06:17,544 --> 00:06:21,915
Meruem: I want an honest answer,
pouf. Give it.

99
00:06:21,982 --> 00:06:23,584
( Shaiapouf gasping )

100
00:06:23,650 --> 00:06:26,920
Meruem: In your
personal opinion,

101
00:06:26,987 --> 00:06:28,422
do you believe
there’s a chance

102
00:06:28,488 --> 00:06:31,024
that these intruders
could best me?

103
00:06:43,604 --> 00:06:45,339
♪

104
00:06:56,149 --> 00:06:59,519
Shaiapouf: No,
never in a million years, sire.

105
00:07:03,557 --> 00:07:07,461
This exceeds
my wildest expectations.

106
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:16,504
Sire, lord meruem,

107
00:07:16,570 --> 00:07:19,406
you are
the very pinnacle of being,

108
00:07:19,473 --> 00:07:22,076
and that much is certain.

109
00:07:29,016 --> 00:07:31,285
Narrator: The aura
was overwhelming,

110
00:07:31,351 --> 00:07:34,254
and as it spread,
it filled knuckle and the others

111
00:07:34,321 --> 00:07:38,392
who were still in hiding
with abject despair.

112
00:07:38,458 --> 00:07:41,328
Knuckle: Whatever this is,

113
00:07:41,395 --> 00:07:45,399
it’s sure as hell
not something we can deal with.

114
00:07:45,465 --> 00:07:47,901
You would need
an entire nation’s military

115
00:07:47,968 --> 00:07:50,971
to handle something
of this magnitude.

116
00:07:51,038 --> 00:07:53,407
Hey, meleoron,
let’s run for it!

117
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:54,607
Meleoron: Seriously?!

118
00:07:54,675 --> 00:07:56,177
Knuckle: You better believe it.

119
00:07:56,243 --> 00:07:57,978
We’ll just head
back to the capital

120
00:07:58,045 --> 00:07:59,413
under the cover of the crowd.

121
00:07:59,479 --> 00:08:02,816
Meleoron: But what about
killua, ikalgo, and the rest?

122
00:08:02,883 --> 00:08:04,551
Knuckle:
There’s nothing we can do.

123
00:08:04,618 --> 00:08:07,121
If they saw that,
they’d understand.

124
00:08:07,187 --> 00:08:09,156
They would run, too.

125
00:08:09,223 --> 00:08:11,158
It’s our only option.

126
00:08:11,225 --> 00:08:12,326
You saw that thing.

127
00:08:13,493 --> 00:08:17,364
No way we can
handle it ourselves.

128
00:08:17,431 --> 00:08:18,899
Meleoron: Well, what if--

129
00:08:18,966 --> 00:08:21,469
what if you and I
were to team up?

130
00:08:21,535 --> 00:08:24,405
Knuckle: We could land
one attack on him, sure.

131
00:08:24,471 --> 00:08:26,273
And if we got really lucky

132
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:29,877
we could probably
even attach a.P.R., but...

133
00:08:31,345 --> 00:08:33,948
The problem is a.P.R.
Only adds interest

134
00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:37,284
to the opponent it’s attached to
if i’m within 50 meters of it,

135
00:08:37,351 --> 00:08:42,289
and if we’re that close to him,
if we’re within his range,

136
00:08:42,356 --> 00:08:44,892
do you really think
we’d last long enough

137
00:08:44,958 --> 00:08:46,893
for the king to go bankrupt?

138
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:50,897
Unless you’ve got the boss’s
lungs, it ain’t happening.

139
00:08:50,964 --> 00:08:53,266
Besides,
the situation’s changed.

140
00:08:53,333 --> 00:08:55,435
It’s not as clear-cut
as it was before.

141
00:08:55,502 --> 00:08:58,305
The enemy knows
about our abilities,

142
00:08:58,372 --> 00:09:01,208
and that means they’re gonna be
good and ready for us.

143
00:09:02,309 --> 00:09:04,845
I was such a freakin’ idiot.

144
00:09:04,912 --> 00:09:07,047
As soon
as the chairman was beaten,

145
00:09:07,114 --> 00:09:08,549
we should have notified
the association

146
00:09:08,615 --> 00:09:10,884
so they could have
started working on plan b

147
00:09:10,951 --> 00:09:13,086
instead of wasting
all this time.

148
00:09:13,153 --> 00:09:14,454
( Meleoron grumbles )

149
00:09:14,521 --> 00:09:15,822
Knuckle: Hurry.

150
00:09:18,325 --> 00:09:21,061
Narrator: Revenge versus duty.

151
00:09:21,128 --> 00:09:23,998
As they continued
to walk along in silence,

152
00:09:24,064 --> 00:09:25,365
the difference
in their motives

153
00:09:25,432 --> 00:09:28,969
placed a growing distance
between them.

154
00:09:31,471 --> 00:09:33,974
Just then...

155
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:37,111
At what seemed
like the speed of light,

156
00:09:37,177 --> 00:09:41,248
meruem’s unparalleled en
lit up the entire palace.

157
00:09:41,315 --> 00:09:43,250
♪

158
00:09:49,256 --> 00:09:52,559
The king, sensing there
were two enemies nearby,

159
00:09:52,626 --> 00:09:54,294
began with knuckle.

160
00:09:58,265 --> 00:10:01,602
Next was meleoron,
knocked unconscious

161
00:10:01,668 --> 00:10:05,405
before he could even think
to activate his power.

162
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,214
( Shaiapouf gasps )

163
00:10:14,281 --> 00:10:16,116
Menthuthuyoupi:
Where’s the king?

164
00:10:19,052 --> 00:10:20,186
Shaiapouf: It’s gone.

165
00:10:22,289 --> 00:10:23,590
( Both gasp )

166
00:10:25,626 --> 00:10:28,963
Meruem: I shall be interrogating
these two later on.

167
00:10:29,029 --> 00:10:31,231
After that,
you can do as you wish.

168
00:10:31,298 --> 00:10:33,233
( Both gasp )

169
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:35,903
Meruem: There were
two other nen users there.

170
00:10:35,969 --> 00:10:39,639
I could sense their aura
reacting to my en,

171
00:10:39,706 --> 00:10:41,341
and I will find them.

172
00:10:41,408 --> 00:10:43,310
♪

173
00:10:46,246 --> 00:10:49,483
Shaiapouf: One of them must be
carrying the unconscious komugi.

174
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:52,420
That has to be where she went.

175
00:10:52,486 --> 00:10:55,122
What do I do? What do I do?

176
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:00,160
( Gasps )

177
00:11:00,227 --> 00:11:03,097
The king, I must stop him.

178
00:11:03,163 --> 00:11:04,464
Sire!

179
00:11:10,304 --> 00:11:13,307
It’s just, if your purpose
is entertainment,

180
00:11:13,373 --> 00:11:15,308
then shouldn’t you
take your time?

181
00:11:15,375 --> 00:11:20,180
Meruem: I get the sense
you have a proposal for me.

182
00:11:20,247 --> 00:11:21,548
Shaiapouf: I do.

183
00:11:21,615 --> 00:11:26,086
Would you be willing
to engage in a game with us?

184
00:11:27,354 --> 00:11:28,288
Meruem: A game?

185
00:11:28,355 --> 00:11:29,556
( High-pitched whine )

186
00:11:29,623 --> 00:11:31,258
Again.

187
00:11:32,993 --> 00:11:35,062
A game.

188
00:11:35,128 --> 00:11:36,630
A game.

189
00:11:40,734 --> 00:11:43,237
♪

190
00:11:43,303 --> 00:11:46,173
Meruem: A game.

191
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,742
A game.

192
00:11:50,744 --> 00:11:53,180
A game of what sort?

193
00:11:53,247 --> 00:11:55,683
Shaiapouf: Youpi and I
will both search for pitou,

194
00:11:55,749 --> 00:11:59,686
and, in the meantime, you look
for the two remaining nen users,

195
00:11:59,753 --> 00:12:04,024
meruem: And we see who can
locate their target first, yes?

196
00:12:04,091 --> 00:12:06,126
- Shaiapouf: Right.
- Menthuthuyoupi: Hold on.

197
00:12:06,193 --> 00:12:09,129
You still need to go and spread
your scales around, don’t you?

198
00:12:09,196 --> 00:12:10,431
Shaiapouf: Yes, that’s correct.

199
00:12:10,497 --> 00:12:13,333
So while I hypnotize
the remaining humans,

200
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:16,470
I would like to make
a request of you, lord meruem.

201
00:12:16,537 --> 00:12:19,240
I ask that you wait here
until I return.

202
00:12:19,306 --> 00:12:22,142
It is painfully obvious
that the difference in power

203
00:12:22,209 --> 00:12:25,345
between yourself and
the intruders is insurmountable.

204
00:12:25,412 --> 00:12:29,516
Finding and capturing them both
will take you but moments,

205
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:31,752
and that isn’t
very entertaining.

206
00:12:31,818 --> 00:12:35,789
Meanwhile, we must find pitou,
who has engaged with the enemy,

207
00:12:35,856 --> 00:12:38,459
and they seem to be capable
of teleportation.

208
00:12:38,525 --> 00:12:42,129
Pitou’s current location
is unknown as of yet.

209
00:12:42,196 --> 00:12:46,100
To make up for the difference,
we’ll need more time.

210
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:49,736
In addition, we ask
for one further handicap.

211
00:12:49,803 --> 00:12:53,240
Meruem: Further handicap?
What is it?

212
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:56,376
Shaiapouf: You will
only be permitted

213
00:12:56,443 --> 00:13:01,148
to use your en once more.
How does that sound, sire?

214
00:13:01,215 --> 00:13:03,050
Menthuthuyoupi: Um...

215
00:13:04,518 --> 00:13:06,086
Meruem: It’s quite amusing.

216
00:13:06,153 --> 00:13:08,088
( Shaiapouf gasps )

217
00:13:08,155 --> 00:13:10,591
Meruem: I like this game.
I will accept.

218
00:13:10,657 --> 00:13:13,093
Shaiapouf: Oh,
thank you very much, sire.

219
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:16,130
Perfect. With this development,

220
00:13:16,196 --> 00:13:19,466
I should have ample time
to kill that girl.

221
00:13:21,535 --> 00:13:24,038
Meruem: And as long
as all of us are playing,

222
00:13:24,104 --> 00:13:26,106
I have a proposal
to make as well.

223
00:13:26,173 --> 00:13:27,408
( Shaiapouf gasps )

224
00:13:27,474 --> 00:13:29,476
Meruem: If you win,
I shall give you a prize.

225
00:13:29,543 --> 00:13:32,312
I will be granting each of you
a single wish.

226
00:13:32,379 --> 00:13:34,314
( Both gasp )

227
00:13:34,381 --> 00:13:35,449
Yes, sire.

228
00:13:35,516 --> 00:13:37,785
Shaiapouf: This is an honor.

229
00:13:37,851 --> 00:13:40,087
Menthuthuyoupi: But, sire,
what do you want

230
00:13:40,153 --> 00:13:41,521
if you win the contest?

231
00:13:41,588 --> 00:13:44,524
Meruem: If I emerge victorious,

232
00:13:44,591 --> 00:13:47,727
you will tell me all that you
have been hiding from me.

233
00:13:47,794 --> 00:13:49,129
Is that understood?

234
00:13:49,196 --> 00:13:50,731
( Both gasp )

235
00:13:50,797 --> 00:13:52,732
♪

236
00:13:57,704 --> 00:13:59,706
- Shaiapouf: But--
- meruem: Silence.

237
00:14:00,807 --> 00:14:02,676
I already told you.

238
00:14:02,743 --> 00:14:06,714
We are all connected.
We share both mind and body.

239
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:11,585
Did you think that I would not
notice your guilt, your anxiety?

240
00:14:11,652 --> 00:14:15,289
You truly feel
I am so oblivious?

241
00:14:15,355 --> 00:14:18,124
However, I sense

242
00:14:18,192 --> 00:14:20,461
that your feelings of loyalty
are stronger now.

243
00:14:23,363 --> 00:14:28,201
Were that not the case, I would
have beheaded you on the spot.

244
00:14:28,268 --> 00:14:31,004
( Shaiapouf whimpers )

245
00:14:31,071 --> 00:14:33,407
( Menthuthuyoupi whimpers )

246
00:14:33,473 --> 00:14:37,610
Meruem: I am certain
you have your reasons.

247
00:14:37,678 --> 00:14:39,380
They’re not my concern.

248
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:43,283
But that is only if I lose.

249
00:14:44,484 --> 00:14:46,419
( Both gasp )

250
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:49,055
Meruem: You will obtain
anything you desire

251
00:14:49,122 --> 00:14:51,391
and retain the freedom
to keep your secret.

252
00:14:51,458 --> 00:14:54,428
You could not wish
for a better set of terms.

253
00:14:54,495 --> 00:14:59,100
That’s only if I lose,
understand?

254
00:15:06,206 --> 00:15:07,974
Shaiapouf:
Thank you, lord meruem.

255
00:15:08,041 --> 00:15:10,744
I shall spread
my scales at once.

256
00:15:10,811 --> 00:15:12,980
I will not waste
a moment’s time.

257
00:15:13,046 --> 00:15:17,050
If we lose this contest,
we will tell you everything.

258
00:15:18,151 --> 00:15:21,087
This I swear on my very life.

259
00:15:21,154 --> 00:15:23,123
( Meruem chuckles )

260
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:26,660
You treat this as more than
mere entertainment, don’t you?

261
00:15:29,363 --> 00:15:33,367
Once pouf has spread his scales
and then returned to the palace,

262
00:15:33,433 --> 00:15:35,368
I shall begin my hunt.

263
00:15:35,435 --> 00:15:37,270
You find this acceptable?

264
00:15:37,337 --> 00:15:38,772
Shaiapouf: I do.

265
00:15:38,839 --> 00:15:40,474
Meruem: Then the victory will go

266
00:15:40,541 --> 00:15:43,611
to whomever returns to this room
with their target first.

267
00:15:43,677 --> 00:15:48,048
If pitou should return while
i’m gone, you are to explain

268
00:15:48,115 --> 00:15:50,250
the objective
of this little contest

269
00:15:50,317 --> 00:15:53,453
and order pitou to hide.
Understood?

270
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,621
Both: Yes, sire!

271
00:15:54,688 --> 00:15:57,424
Meruem: The two nen users
my en sensed

272
00:15:57,491 --> 00:15:59,727
were an octopus
and a human being,

273
00:15:59,793 --> 00:16:03,330
who seem to be carrying
some sort of burden.

274
00:16:05,432 --> 00:16:07,267
Shaiapouf: I must win.

275
00:16:07,334 --> 00:16:11,271
No, victory is already assured.

276
00:16:11,338 --> 00:16:13,640
The only question now is,

277
00:16:13,707 --> 00:16:16,243
what should be done
about pitou and the girl?

278
00:16:19,713 --> 00:16:21,281
Menthuthuyoupi: Ready?

279
00:16:21,348 --> 00:16:22,683
Shaiapouf: Let us begin!

280
00:16:22,749 --> 00:16:25,051
♪

281
00:16:28,155 --> 00:16:31,058
Menthuthuyoupi: So where do
you think pitou ran off to?

282
00:16:31,124 --> 00:16:32,225
Shaiapouf: It’s all right.

283
00:16:32,292 --> 00:16:34,094
Pitou should be back
before long.

284
00:16:34,161 --> 00:16:37,197
Turn around, and go wait
over by the west tower

285
00:16:37,264 --> 00:16:39,133
until pitou has returned.

286
00:16:39,199 --> 00:16:41,501
Then wait.
Do not go near the king.

287
00:16:41,568 --> 00:16:44,304
Menthuthuyoupi: Fine,
but you can’t use segments

288
00:16:44,371 --> 00:16:46,039
while you spread your scales,

289
00:16:46,106 --> 00:16:48,008
so you really
aren’t buying us any time.

290
00:16:48,075 --> 00:16:51,612
Shaiapouf: Place your trust
in me. I will not fail!

291
00:16:51,678 --> 00:16:53,046
Menthuthuyoupi: Hmm.

292
00:16:58,485 --> 00:17:01,421
( Palm panting )

293
00:17:01,488 --> 00:17:05,325
Unbelievable.
Such ferocious aura.

294
00:17:06,426 --> 00:17:08,295
Those two are dead.

295
00:17:08,362 --> 00:17:12,366
No, they’re still alive,
for now, anyway.

296
00:17:12,432 --> 00:17:15,035
They were
only knocked unconscious.

297
00:17:15,102 --> 00:17:16,370
But where is gon?

298
00:17:16,436 --> 00:17:19,272
Killua’s carrying him.

299
00:17:19,339 --> 00:17:22,375
Long hair? Is it someone else?

300
00:17:22,442 --> 00:17:26,579
No, those are the only
two figures in my crystal ball.

301
00:17:26,647 --> 00:17:28,382
That must be gon.

302
00:17:28,448 --> 00:17:31,117
Something must have happened
when I wasn’t watching.

303
00:17:31,185 --> 00:17:33,387
Where’s pitou?

304
00:17:33,453 --> 00:17:37,991
In any case,
don’t come back here, please.

305
00:17:38,058 --> 00:17:39,993
Pouf is spreading scales

306
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:42,396
on the people
gathered before the palace.

307
00:17:42,462 --> 00:17:44,531
Are they poisonous?

308
00:17:44,598 --> 00:17:48,001
It would be better for me
if he’d stay near the king.

309
00:17:48,068 --> 00:17:51,505
In any case, he’s on
the other side of the palace.

310
00:17:51,572 --> 00:17:55,009
I must get as far from
my previous location as I can.

311
00:17:55,075 --> 00:17:59,212
After that wave of en,
I immediately used wink blue,

312
00:17:59,279 --> 00:18:02,582
as soon as I did,
the king appeared next to pouf,

313
00:18:02,649 --> 00:18:05,085
carrying both knuckle
and meleoron.

314
00:18:05,152 --> 00:18:08,522
Only a few seconds had passed.
I’m sure of it.

315
00:18:10,424 --> 00:18:13,327
He’ll be coming after ikalgo
or me next.

316
00:18:13,393 --> 00:18:16,496
The king could be
standing behind me even now.

317
00:18:16,563 --> 00:18:19,332
I have to hurry and
get even farther away

318
00:18:19,399 --> 00:18:21,635
before the king uses en again.

319
00:18:24,238 --> 00:18:26,974
I have to go in there.

320
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:29,376
If i’m crossing the plain
when he uses en,

321
00:18:29,443 --> 00:18:31,979
I won’t be able to escape.

322
00:18:32,045 --> 00:18:33,747
If i’m deep underground,

323
00:18:33,814 --> 00:18:36,750
perhaps his en
won’t be able to reach me.

324
00:18:36,817 --> 00:18:39,987
But i’m not giving myself
an escape route.

325
00:18:40,053 --> 00:18:42,455
Should I stay outside
of the palace instead

326
00:18:42,523 --> 00:18:44,992
and hope that the king doesn’t
make his move for a while?

327
00:18:45,058 --> 00:18:47,761
But there’s no reason
to think he won’t.

328
00:18:49,463 --> 00:18:51,398
( Panting )

329
00:18:54,768 --> 00:18:56,303
What should I do?

330
00:18:56,370 --> 00:18:58,172
What’s the right decision?

331
00:19:00,674 --> 00:19:01,608
( Gasps )

332
00:19:01,675 --> 00:19:03,644
Ikalgo!

333
00:19:03,710 --> 00:19:05,278
Ikalgo: I figured you’d be here.

334
00:19:05,345 --> 00:19:07,547
Come on!
Let’s get inside! Hurry up!

335
00:19:07,614 --> 00:19:09,116
Palm: Yes, but how--

336
00:19:09,183 --> 00:19:11,719
ikalgo: Come on.
Isn’t that why you came here?

337
00:19:11,785 --> 00:19:14,488
If he uses his en again,
we’re finished.

338
00:19:21,161 --> 00:19:22,362
Where’s killua?

339
00:19:22,429 --> 00:19:24,731
Palm: He ran off
to go find gon.

340
00:19:24,798 --> 00:19:26,366
They’re together now.

341
00:19:26,433 --> 00:19:30,103
I don’t know
what happened to pitou.

342
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:31,338
Ikalgo: Hmm.

343
00:19:35,442 --> 00:19:37,344
♪

344
00:19:38,445 --> 00:19:39,613
I see.

345
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:42,650
So meleoron and knuckle
were captured.

346
00:19:44,251 --> 00:19:46,987
The king is
on a whole other level.

347
00:19:47,054 --> 00:19:48,355
( Palm grunts )

348
00:19:50,057 --> 00:19:51,225
Ikalgo: He spared them.

349
00:19:51,291 --> 00:19:53,160
Any idea why he’d do that?

350
00:19:53,227 --> 00:19:56,030
Palm: I can’t say.

351
00:19:56,096 --> 00:19:58,765
It’s possible
it’s just wishful thinking,

352
00:19:58,832 --> 00:20:01,401
but I think they’re still alive.

353
00:20:01,468 --> 00:20:03,203
Ikalgo: They’re alive, huh?

354
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:06,006
Probably so they can be traded.

355
00:20:06,073 --> 00:20:09,777
( Palm gasps ) As hostages,
like killua mentioned?

356
00:20:11,078 --> 00:20:13,180
Ikalgo: I’ll set a trap.

357
00:20:13,247 --> 00:20:17,017
There’s no way
i’m gonna let this end here.

358
00:20:17,084 --> 00:20:18,652
But first things first.

359
00:20:18,719 --> 00:20:21,522
We need to hide the girl
in bizeff’s room.

360
00:20:21,588 --> 00:20:22,789
( Palm sighs )

361
00:20:22,856 --> 00:20:25,025
♪

362
00:21:00,327 --> 00:21:02,196
( High-pitched whine )

363
00:21:09,469 --> 00:21:12,205
Meruem: A game.

364
00:21:12,272 --> 00:21:14,708
♪

365
00:21:14,775 --> 00:21:16,543
A game.

366
00:21:25,452 --> 00:21:27,154
( Singing in Japanese )

